他们之间的区别是什么","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915085","replies":60,"created_ts":1676077183,"created":"08:59:43","title":"全球通，神州行还有动感地带？移动你是真会玩啊","author":"strp","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/strp","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a2b2133c9ec1084a9c2884696ecf4f1a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":915216,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p>搞了一下午，想在部署了 docker 的机器上搞个透明代理，看了一天也没看懂 docker 的 nat 是怎么配的，模拟怎么也跑不通</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://file.renwuzhi.wiki/images/12.png\"/></p>\n<p>话说有了第一条规则后，后面的规则还有屁用啊</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915216","replies":52,"created_ts":1676113558,"created":"19:05:58","title":"iptables 太他妈难用了","author":"huiyanpohundh123","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/huiyanpohundh123","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/93ce/0383/533241_mini.png?m=1671678730"},{"id":915142,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"<p>在家办公，一直坐在电脑前面写代码就很累，想写一下到床上换 mbp 接着写，就感觉没必要提交。</p>\n<p>手上有有群晖的 DS920+，千兆路由。代码两台电脑都有的时候，双向同步挺快的。\n但新项目，比如前端 yarn 一下，同步就一个小时了。</p>\n<p>大佬们有没有好办法让代码这种小文件快速同步。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915142","replies":51,"created_ts":1676094923,"created":"13:55:23","title":"请问在家怎么让两台电脑通过 NAS 快速同步代码","author":"zau11berer","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zau11berer","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b581cd33e76828dd5906ad76d43abac8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":915115,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"<p>大佬们，推荐下 NAS 系统呗</p>\n<p>目前已购买：天宝 amd 300u （ 2 盘位，4 个千兆网口）+8g 内存+128g 固态+4T 酷鹰硬盘，我的需求是\n1 、下载电影，bt 、Aria2\n2 、远程同步公司的文件\n3 、软路由实现科学+去广告\n4 、手机、平板内网看电影</p>\n<p>目前了解到的系统有，esxi+黑群晖（ sata 直通好像有问题）、pve+黑群晖、istoreOS （文件同步相关插件要收费）、unraid 、truenas</p>\n<p>我第一次玩 nas ，有 linux 基础，大佬们帮我参谋下</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915115","replies":39,"created_ts":1676087417,"created":"11:50:17","title":"大佬们，推荐下 NAS 系统呗","author":"EchoGroot","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/EchoGroot","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ed9fe86ce9a20cf94bba186ebd432261?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":915161,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>有时候想买一些国外的服务，比如 google colab 之类的，需要 visa 卡，现在学生一枚，试过申请中行的，被拒得很快</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915161","replies":36,"created_ts":1676100719,"created":"15:31:59","title":"学生现在有办法申请 visa 卡吗","author":"bybyte","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/bybyte","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5da5/be8a/538614_mini.png?m=1669730303"},{"id":915108,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>小米电视自带的配置跟不上了，打算搞个盒子：</p>\n<p>1 配置尽可能高点 4+32 起吧，CPU 主流一点，可玩性高点（大概率就拿来当盒子用），千兆网口，USB3+，散热给力。</p>\n<p>2 原生系统不要包含类似小米这种商业信息，自带个给力播放器、文件管理啥的就够了。</p>\n<p>3 视频流畅支持 4K ，支持尽可能多的编码，平时看爱优腾+本地+Alist</p>\n<p>4 遥控器能替代电视自带的遥控器，否则开电视用一个，接着切换源，然后再换成盒子遥控器，太折磨人了。</p>\n<p>5 流畅、耐用。</p>\n<p>6 价格 400 以内。</p>\n<p>目前搜了搜有几个心仪的：</p>\n<p>1 x96 max +：遥控器傻大粗，而且变种很多，TB 挑花眼。</p>\n<p>2 HK1 BOX：同上，便众多，升级版啥的，还有说散热不好。</p>\n<p>3 极客库：TB 就 2 款，倒是不纠结，就是好像没啥声音。</p>\n<p>大伙给点意见。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915108","replies":36,"created_ts":1676084851,"created":"11:07:31","title":"推荐一个当下性价比高的电视盒子","author":"wangxiaoaer","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangxiaoaer","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4726a1e637f3210184a90f9a29963a6b?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":915061,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","description":"m1pro 版 mbp 。目前看中了罗技 master3s ，在罗技京东自营店看到正常款 599 ，mac 适用款 899 ，客服说 m1 芯片最好用后者，兼容性好些。在其他店（京东淘宝 pdd 都看了）好像都没有看到专门的 mac 款（ 3 有，3s 没），不知有无区别。以及求问 3s 和 3 区别大吗，有没有必要买 3s ？如有其他鼠标也欢迎推荐！","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915061","replies":36,"created_ts":1676046703,"created":"00:31:43","title":"mbp 鼠标推荐","author":"vftj","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vftj","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a80c0ba9c86a04b9c829323e4388edf4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":915178,"node":"优惠信息","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/deals","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8d31/7bdc/747_mini.png?m=1523201604","description":"<p>pdd 百亿补贴 口令如下</p>\n<p>1:/⇥8TNsmPYBeTcsw⇤ 复制并打开拼多多 APP ，849 元购买百亿补贴 [ 3 人团] 海康存储 C4000 2TB SSD 固态硬盘 M.2 接口(NVMe 协议 PCIe 4.0 x4)，仅剩 2 个名额</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>我个人有需求买，但是只有 3 人团才有这个价格，所以有意买的朋友看过来～</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915178","replies":35,"created_ts":1676104755,"created":"16:39:15","title":"海康 C4000 2T 三人团 848，有一起的吗？（还差两位）","author":"287854442","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/287854442","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d95b/6d57/26655_mini.png?m=1592360490"},{"id":915082,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>很魔幻，apple pencil 一直犹豫没下单</p>\n<p>jd ，tb ，pdd 来回看，jd900 左右，tb 没看到好价，pdd 百亿 869</p>\n<p>但是冲浪看到很多人 700 多在 pdd 拿下就没下单</p>\n<p>刚刚再看价格 ，突然发券，800-80 ，速降 789🥹马上下单</p>\n<p>这波难道是检测到我想在别的地方买，然后发券了么？</p>\n<p>同理，之前看到有人分享在瑞幸加购咖啡一直不下单，也会有券发（真假存疑</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/915082","replies":33,"created_ts":1676075790,"created":"08:36:30","title":"pdd 百亿补贴的券是个什么原理？","author":"jasmineaaaaa","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jasmineaaaaa","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e22f/63f1/577109_mini.png?m=1674978406"},{"id":915097,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>大半夜身上发烫，突醒，然后一直睡不着，能感觉到脸烫。\n早上起来身上就不烫了，但是发冷，四肢关节点会痛，感觉很沉。\n头很晕，很像上次阳了的初期症状。</p>\n","u